{"tid":1025243,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟分享下自己/另一半做過on9而又好笑嘅事","createTime":"2019-02-17T08:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T14:45:59.000Z","uid":113546,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa57e5a6b742a0b06ff4c891c9c198ea35dab11","tid":1025243,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:10:45.000Z","msg":"同ex拍拖𠴱時 佢wts搵我 但我掛住打機潛水<br />\n然後有個wts group 係佢家姐呀哥都喺入面嘅 就傾緊果期去旅行啲嘢<br />\n我就懶有交戴噉 話我打緊機 唔好比女朋友知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我唔記得女朋友都喺個group到<br />\n所以佢睇到我講啲咩<br />\n然後....佢嬲咗<br />\n<br />\n到嬲完之後拎返出嚟講 我地都笑到傻咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲好記得開頭佢嬲 到之後嬲完拎返出嚟笑<br />\n我笑到摟住佢 用面面磨佢面面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好幸福<br />\n可惜已經過去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baa8f0f43631b09a36f15a260e84eb2795dd9d4","tid":1025243,"uid":210182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"好sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8718a6dc67e78f72b00a96b3a11a0d17d35a1e4","tid":1025243,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7baa8f0f43631b09a36f15a260e84eb2795dd9d4","tid":1025243,"uid":210182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"好sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"你都可以㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打加油"},{"pid":"bd3c8d6e834c2864f1f6f08757a3b712191c26a8","tid":1025243,"uid":210182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8718a6dc67e78f72b00a96b3a11a0d17d35a1e4","tid":1025243,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7baa8f0f43631b09a36f15a260e84eb2795dd9d4","tid":1025243,"uid":210182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:38